Achievements.Name: Style Master
Achievements.Description: Campaign: Perform a GREAT take off or a PERFECT landing on the normal hill!

Achievements.Name: Speed Junkie
Achievements.Description: Campaign: Go faster than 155 km/h in Downhill!

Achievements.Name: Eagle Eye
Achievements.Description: Campaign: In Curling, shoot the rear stone out of the house without touching the front one!

Achievements.Name: Finger Stroboscope
Achievements.Description: Campaign: Hit 20 targets at the Biathlon shooting! The counter resets every 5 seconds.

Achievements.Name: Skeletorious
Achievements.Description: Campaign: Go faster than 116 km/h in Skeleton!

Achievements.Name: Downhill Boss
Achievements.Description: Campaign: Be faster than the favorite in Downhill!

Achievements.Name: Mr. and Mrs. Skill
Achievements.Description: Campaign: Get the Curling stone onto the specified position without touching your other stone.

Achievements.Name: Paceman
Achievements.Description: Campaign: Reach a top speed of at least 60 km/h at Biathlon.

Achievements.Name: AIR G
Achievements.Description: Campaign: Jump over 50 meters in Super G. Search the best ramp on the track!

Achievements.Name: Brainiac
Achievements.Description: Campaign: Add up the figures during the run within 135 seconds and enter the correct result!

Achievements.Name: Quick Start
Achievements.Description: Campaign: You need to perform an awesome start (better than 89%) in Speed Skating!

Achievements.Name: Speedskate Boss
Achievements.Description: Campaign: Beat the Boss in 500m Speed Skating! Mind the racing line!

Achievements.Name: Ruler
Achievements.Description: Campaign: You have 35 seconds to overtake all 7 opponents at Biathlon.

Achievements.Name: Bob Perfect
Achievements.Description: Campaign: Perform a perfect start with the four-seater bob.

Achievements.Name: MC Fly
Achievements.Description: Campaign: Keep cool, watch your style and perform a GREAT landing!

Achievements.Name: Golden Moments
Achievements.Description: Campaign: Collect 37 gold coins in Downhill. You have 150 seconds.

Achievements.Name: Clever
Achievements.Description: Campaign: Add up the figures during the run within 135 seconds and enter the correct result!

Achievements.Name: Bob Boss
Achievements.Description: Campaign: Match with the fast as lightning two-seater bob champion and beat him!

Achievements.Name: Sniper
Achievements.Description: Campaign: Shoot two adversarial stones out of the house without touching other stones!

Achievements.Name: Rhythm Sticks
Achievements.Description: Campaign: Great rhythm (over 90%) in 500m Speed Skating! Hit GREAT or PERFECT every time.

Achievements.Name: Art of Curling
Achievements.Description: Campaign: Show your feeling for art and match the given pattern with your Curling stones!

Achievements.Name: Untouchable
Achievements.Description: Campaign: Race through the ice canal without touching the boards!

Achievements.Name: Skull Skill
Achievements.Description: Campaign: Avoid any contact with the skulls in this 500 m Speed Skating race and win the race!

Achievements.Name: Giant Slalom Boss
Achievements.Description: Campaign: You compete with Mr. Giant Slalom himself! Win and you'll be unforgotten.

Achievements.Name: Kamikaze
Achievements.Description: Campaign: Fall as hard as you can after jumping 130 m from the large hill.

Achievements.Name: Yin and Yang
Achievements.Description: Campaign: Collect 42 coins but avoid the skulls. You have 112 seconds!

Achievements.Name: Art of Shooting
Achievements.Description: Campaign:  Be the van Gogh of the track and shoot the right patterns in Biathlon.

Achievements.Name: Skiller
Achievements.Description: Campaign: You have two stones to remove three adversarial stones from the house. Good luck!

Achievements.Name: Calculator
Achievements.Description: Campaign: Add up the figures during the run within 100 seconds and enter the correct result!

Achievements.Name: Biathlon Boss
Achievements.Description: Campaign: Compete with the best biathlete of all times! Losing is not an option!

Achievements.Name: High Skiller
Achievements.Description: Campaign: Push the opponent's stones to the specified position without moving your stones!

Achievements.Name: Alpha Dog
Achievements.Description: Campaign: Keep your position for 60 seconds. No one must overtake you!

Achievements.Name: Skully
Achievements.Description: Campaign: Avoid all skulls within the given time without getting disqualified!

Achievements.Name: Style Flyer
Achievements.Description: Campaign: Get an excellent style score at the Ski Jump from the small hill.

Achievements.Name: Time of the Skull
Achievements.Description: Campaign: Avoid the skulls within the time limit!

Achievements.Name: Slalom Boss
Achievements.Description: Campaign: Do your best in Slalom! Defeat one of the best athletes in the world.
